    "instruction": "Load metric.csv, trace.csv, log.csv, and error_logs.csv. For each file, return a compact summary: total row count, top up to 20 unique values of the component column (cmdb_id) with their counts, and top up to 20 unique KPI/trace/log names (kpi_name for metric.csv, trace_name for trace.csv, log_name for log.csv, and message sample counts for error_logs.csv) with their counts. Also include the overall time range (min and max timestamp) present in each file. Keep outputs tabular and limited to top 20 rows per list."
